Text: Thanks kindly, JW! Have a safe weekend everyone - see ya back on Monday.

JW what is the best way to get in touch with you? I was wondering if you still have Mark Levin's shows from '08? I am trying to find a copy of them and I see you have them posted (but no seeds) and was wondering if you still have the files -  would you consider bundling them by the year or half year and posting them so I can download them? Please let me know. My email is wisenheimer@outgun.com Thanks.
Wisenheimer, I'm sorry, but I don't have any shows that old. In fact, I only seed for 5 days. I don't know where you could go to get them except for Rush's paid site. Sorry.
